{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Giacomo Debidda","author":"Giacomo Debidda"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6227b76c-0adc-5f26-b9a0-95fd62a0891d >>> MarkdownRemark","excerpt":"Last week I started working on a new visualization and I wanted to include a couple of d3 plugins:  d3-legend  by Susie Lu and  d3-line…","html":"<p>Last week I started working on a new visualization and I wanted to include a couple of d3 plugins: <a href=\"http://d3-legend.susielu.com/\">d3-legend</a> by Susie Lu and <a href=\"https://peterbeshai.com/vis/d3-line-chunked/\">d3-line-chunked</a> by Peter Beshai.</p>\n<p>I spent some time figuring out how to include these plugins with webpack, so I’m writing this small reminder here.</p>\n<p>As far as I know, there are at least 3 ways to import d3 and some plugins.</p>\n<h2>The wrong way to do it</h2>\n<pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--import syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>import</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--variable syntax--language syntax--import-all syntax--js\"><span>*</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>as</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--variable syntax--other syntax--module-alias syntax--js\"><span>d3</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>from</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--string syntax--quoted syntax--single syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--begin syntax--js\"><span>&#39;</span></span><span>d3</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--end syntax--js\"><span>&#39;</span></span></span></span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--terminator syntax--statement syntax--js\"><span>;</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--import syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>import</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--variable syntax--language syntax--import-all syntax--js\"><span>*</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>as</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--variable syntax--other syntax--module-alias syntax--js\"><span>d3Legend</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>from</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--string syntax--quoted syntax--single syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--begin syntax--js\"><span>&#39;</span></span><span>d3-svg-legend</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--end syntax--js\"><span>&#39;</span></span></span></span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--terminator syntax--statement syntax--js\"><span>;</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--import syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>import</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--variable syntax--language syntax--import-all syntax--js\"><span>*</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>as</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--variable syntax--other syntax--module-alias syntax--js\"><span>d3LineChunked</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>from</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--string syntax--quoted syntax--single syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--begin syntax--js\"><span>&#39;</span></span><span>d3-line-chunked</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--end syntax--js\"><span>&#39;</span></span></span></span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--terminator syntax--statement syntax--js\"><span>;</span></span></span></div></pre>\n<p>This is bad for 2 reasons:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>we are importing the entire d3 library</li>\n<li>the plugins are not attached to <code class=\"language-text\">d3</code>, so in order to use them we have to do something like this: <code class=\"language-text\">const colorLegend = d3Legend.legendColor()</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>The lazy way to do it</h2>\n<pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--import syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>import</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--variable syntax--language syntax--import-all syntax--js\"><span>*</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>as</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--variable syntax--other syntax--module-alias syntax--js\"><span>d3Base</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>from</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--string syntax--quoted syntax--single syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--begin syntax--js\"><span>&#39;</span></span><span>d3</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--end syntax--js\"><span>&#39;</span></span></span></span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--terminator syntax--statement syntax--js\"><span>;</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--import syntax--js\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--js\"><span>import</span></span><sp